    "description": "This fiery feast is inspired by traditional Xi'an flavour. You'll coat chicken thighs in a Xi'an-inspired blend of toasted salt and pepper chilli seasoning before frying till crispy. Serve up with steamed rice and a spicy smashed cucumber salad.",
